    {
      "id": "1ae4750c-f3ba-805b-88ea-e19303c02aca",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Comparison of the 3 algorithms is done against different baseline approaches - random and grouping based on course score. Simulating the results on data from previous years shows that the grouping algorithms could lead to better results on the evaluation metrics than the alternative methods.",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
